data.description:
One of Pride's crossing's best homes! This large 5 bedroom home is turn-key and ready for years of enjoyment. It offers a new roof, newer carpet, beautiful hardwood floors and a brand new furnace. The basement is finished and ready for Monday night football. The large family room is complete with a bar and an extra large area that could be used for an exercise space or craft area. There is a 5th bedroom and 3/4 bath downstairs as well. The main level is just awesome and boasts a large family room, formal dining room and living room. It is a very happy home with lots of natural light. The back yard offers a large patio and pergola. The location is extremely convenient within close proximity to shopping, trails and parks. Not to mention, this home is in the Cherry Creek School District. You won't be disappointed.
